divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking sunrise pictures at a public boat landing in Savannah, GA, known as Bell's Landing. One of the many pictures i took that morning was of a bird sitting on a wooden post. It wasn't until I downloaded the pictures onto my computer that I noticed this object in the background. When I first noticed the object I immediately thought of a UFO. I cannot comment on the UFO's movements as I did not notice it until I downloaded the picture.
